ZH: 苍穹是天空的另一个称呼。
EN: "Cangqiong" is another name for the sky.

ZH: 他仰望着苍穹，思考着人生的意义。
EN: He looked up at the sky and pondered the meaning of life.

ZH: 苍穹中的星星璀璨夺目。
EN: The stars in the sky are dazzling.

ZH: 每当我看到苍穹，我就感到无比的宁静。
EN: Whenever I look at the sky, I feel incredibly peaceful.

ZH: 小孩子们在草地上仰望着苍穹，追逐着遥远的梦想。
EN: Children look up at the sky and chase after distant dreams on the grass.

ZH: 天空中的苍穹流动着朝霞。
EN: The sky is filled with the flow of morning glow.

ZH: 在那片苍穹下，我们相遇了。
EN: We met under that sky.

ZH: 他一直在寻找一片属于自己的苍穹。
EN: He has been searching for his own sky.

ZH: 他们手拉手走在苍穹之下，快乐地笑着。
EN: They walk hand in hand under the sky, laughing happily.

ZH: 苍穹中的云彩变幻多姿。
EN: The clouds in the sky change in various ways.

ZH: 深夜的苍穹中耀眼的月亮照亮了大地。
EN: The bright moon in the sky illuminates the earth in the late night.

ZH: 苍穹中的飞鸟展翅高飞。
EN: Birds in the sky spread their wings and soar.

ZH: 漫步在苍穹之下，我感受到了自由的力量。
EN: Walking under the sky, I feel the power of freedom.

ZH: 黄昏时分，苍穹之上布满了绚烂的晚霞。
EN: At dusk, the sky is filled with vibrant evening glow.

ZH: 他凝视着苍穹，希望那里的星星能听到他的祈祷。
EN: He gazes at the sky, hoping that the stars there can hear his prayers.

ZH: 苍穹之下一片宁静，只有微风的声音回荡在耳边。
EN: Under the sky, there is tranquility, with only the sound of the gentle breeze echoing in the ears.

ZH:她追逐着心中的苍穹，勇往直前。
EN: She chases after the sky in her heart, moving forward bravely.

ZH: 在苍穹之下，我们共同见证了时光的流转。
EN: Under the sky, we witnessed the passage of time together.

ZH: 若干年后，我们还会再相会在苍穹之下。
EN: We will meet again under the sky after many years.

ZH: 无论走到哪里，苍穹永远都在我们身边。
EN: Wherever we go, the sky is always by our side.
